{"name":"image-replacement","versionType":"4.4","type":"utilities","group":"utilities","basename":"image-replacement.md","relpath":"4.4/utilities/image-replacement.json","attributes":{"layout":"docs","title":"Image replacement","description":"Swap text for background images with the image replacement class.","group":"utilities"},"html":"<h1 class=\"bd-title\" id=\"content\">Image replacement</h1><p class=\"bd-lead\">Swap text for background images with the image replacement class.</p><div class=\"bd-callout bd-callout-warning\"><h5 id=\"warning\">Warning</h5>\n<p>The <code>text-hide()</code> class and mixin has been deprecated as of v4.1. It will be removed entirely in v5.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n<p>Utilize the <code>.text-hide</code> class or mixin to help replace an element&#39;s text content with a background image.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-html\">\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text-hide<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Custom heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-scss\">\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Usage as a mixin</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heading </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">@include</span> text-hide<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n</figure>\n<p>Use the <code>.text-hide</code> class to maintain the accessibility and SEO benefits of heading tags, but want to utilize a <code>background-image</code> instead of text.</p>\n<div class=\"bd-example\">\n  <h1 class=\"text-hide\" style=\"background-image: url('/docs//assets/brand/bootstrap-solid.svg'); width: 50px; height: 50px;\">Bootstrap</h1>\n</div>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-html\">\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text-hide<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'...'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Bootstrap<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n</figure>\n"}